Layouts
- Keep `app/(app)/layout.tsx` lean; global chrome only. Avoid per-page logic here.

Metadata
- Use `generateMetadata` for dynamic titles/meta. Avoid client-only side effects for SEO.

Navigation
- Use `next/navigation` hooks for client transitions; prefer `Link` over `a` tags.
